HEADWORD: Mining
<hw>Min"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Mine</er>,
<pos>v. i.</pos>]</ety> <def>The act or business of making mines or of
working them.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mining</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Mining
<hw>Min"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to mines; <as>as,
<ex>mining</ex> engineer; <ex>mining</ex> machinery; a <ex>mining</ex>
region.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Mining engineering</b></col>. <cd>See the Note under
<er>Engineering</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Minion</ent>⟦br⟧
